{
 "name": "RPlog_Glitterstim_Withdrawal",
 "title": "Glitterstim Withdrawal",
 "summary": "At the darkened Vichten Estate, Axel Vichten hosts a dinner for the OOAG auditor Malif and the exiled Imperial physician Lynae Cassius. Axel presents Malif with a grisly gift -- the severed thumbs of Tyy'sun Eson, taken in revenge -- and lays out his plans to wage a covert war against the Zhao Maffi on behalf of the Sith, soliciting Malif's intelligence and Lynae's discreet medical services for those who carry his broken-spear card. Over rare meats and Corellian wine the three trade hard truths about loyalty, trust, and the costs of their bloodstained pasts. Mid-conversation Axel collapses into a severe glitterstim withdrawal, weeping and bleeding from the nose; Lynae tends him while Malif insists the affliction is a Dark Force taint and that Axel is force-sensitive, urging him into the life-rich garden. They relocate Axel to the thickest part of the vineyard, where droids bring a medkit and Lynae begins to manage his symptoms, and Malif warns him to stay clear of Malign and all Force adepts until he is clean.",
